snippet.title: Steins;Gate - North American Trailer | PS3, PS Vita
snippet.description:
The highly acclaimed award-winning visual novel comes to North America on PlayStation 3 and PS Vita in August! Join Okabe Rintaro and his group of teenage scientists as they become embroiled in a time travel conspiracy, pursued by the evil and shady Organization, and locked into a worldline where the future of humanity is bleak. Developed by 5pb. and Nitroplus, Steins;Gate was awarded Famitsu magizine's coveted annual Game of Excellence award and was voted one of the most emotionally charged games ever made. 

Rated Mature: Blood, Partial Nudity, Sexual Themes, Strong Language, Violence

http://www.pqube.co.uk/steinsgate/

Steins;Gate 2009 - 2015 MAGES./5pb./Nitroplus. Licensed to GAME RIGHTS MANAGEMENT and published by PQube LTD.
